To collect, first scatter. To Weaken, first strengthen. To abolish, first
 establish. To conclude, first initiate.
This is called subtle illumination. Soft and weak overcome stiff and
 strong.
Fish cannot escape the deep pool. A country's sharpest weapons Cannot be
 displayed.
